Metcon:“10 Plagues of Panda!”For time:1 – Wall Walk2 – DeadLifts (120/70kg)3 – Toes to bar4 – Burpees5 – Wallball Shots (#10/6)6 – Ring Dips7 – Box Jumps8 – Pullups9 – Kettlebell Swings (#32/24)10 – Ring Muscle-Ups
*After completing the first movement go back to 1 and begin again adding a new movement each round. There are 10 total rounds with one new movement being added each round. In example: Do 1 Wall Walk, then 1 Wall Walk + 2 DeadLifts, then 1 Wall Walk + 2 DeadLifts + 3 Toes-to-bar etc…
